svg.desc: Output from Flights of Ideas SVG Sketchup Plugin

g.aria-label: Hold down the button and rotate the knob (brightness changes only affect your heart)
Blue: Connected to the internet, but Blaine is offline
Red: Cannot connect to the internet. Will keep retrying in background. Reboot to change wifi network (setup mode)

Orange/Yellow: Setup Mode (could not connect to previously saved wifi). On your phone/laptop, connect to the wifi called "Chelsey Heart Setup", and if not automatically redirected, go to 192.168.4.1 in a web browser. Or reboot to retry connecting to previously saved wifi
